sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Optimizer
    participant A as Analyzer LLM
    participant W as Worktree (per candidate)
    participant C as Inner coding agent
    participant T as Tools (read/edit/bash/...)
    participant S as Subprocess runner
    participant E as Evaluator
    O->>A: diagnose(case_results, bundle, weights)
    A-->>O: M plans { focus_area, PROMPT.md, plan.json }
    loop for each candidate
        O->>W: git worktree add
        O->>C: launch with PROMPT.md, MAX_STEPS=50
        loop ≤50 steps
            C->>T: tool call (e.g. edit)
            T->>T: FileTracker.assert_fresh()<br/>(mtime+size check)
            T-->>C: ToolResult
            Note over C: doom-loop guard: same call 3× → abort
        end
        C-->>O: edits applied
        O->>S: spawn agent subprocess (uv venv)<br/>inject W3C traceparent
        S-->>E: per-case outputs + spans
        E->>E: 4-layer score<br/>(mech · LLM-judge · tools · type)
        E-->>O: score.json { avg_total }
    end
    O->>O: accept_step gates<br/>read-only byte-eq · complexity · holdout
    O->>O: snapshot accepted code
